@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Assignment Staging - EduNexus</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Synchronized with EduNexus */
            --primary: #5c24ff;
            --primary-light: #9b8cf8;
            --primary-lighter: #f0edff;
            --bg-color: #fafafa;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #111827;
            --text-muted: #6b7280;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --success: #10b981;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
            --ai-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #5c24ff 0%, #d946ef 100%);
            --radius-md: 8px;
            --radius-lg: 12px;
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Topbar */
        .topbar {
            height: 70px;
            background-color: var(--surface);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 40px;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .back-btn {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .ai-status-badge {
            background: var(--primary-lighter);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .topbar-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(155, 140, 248, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(92, 36, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Layout */
        .staging-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .editor-col {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .ai-col {
            width: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        /* Notice Banner */
        .ai-banner {
            background: #faf5ff;
            border: 1px solid #e9d5ff;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 16px 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .ai-banner-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            background: var(--ai-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .ai-banner-content h4 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6b21a8;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .ai-banner-content p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7e22ce;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Main Editor */
        .title-input {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            outline: none;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .title-input:focus {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
        }

        .card-section {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section-header {
            padding: 16px 24px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .editor-toolbar {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background-color: var(--surface);
        }

        .toolbar-btn {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .toolbar-btn:hover {
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .editor-content {
            padding: 24px;
            min-height: 200px;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        /* Generated Rubric Table */
        .rubric-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .rubric-table th, .rubric-table td {
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .rubric-table th {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background: #fafafa;
        }

        .rubric-table td {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .rubric-table input {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            outline: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: transparent;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .rubric-table input:focus, .rubric-table input:hover {
            border-color: var(--border);
            background: var(--surface);
        }

        .rubric-table .pts-input {
            width: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* AI Assistant Sidebar */
        .assistant-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: sticky;
            top: 110px;
        }

        .assistant-header {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .assistant-header i {
            background: var(--ai-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .prompt-info {
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .prompt-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .prompt-bubble {
            background: var(--primary-lighter);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .suggestions-list {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .suggestion-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            transition: 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .suggestion-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
            background: var(--surface);
        }

        .suggestion-item i {
            color: #d946ef;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .suggestion-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .ai-chat-input {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .chat-box {
            position: relative;
        }

        .chat-textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 12px 48px 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: inherit;
            outline: none;
            resize: none;
            height: 80px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .chat-textarea:focus {
            border-color: #d946ef;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(217, 70, 239, 0.1);
        }

        .send-btn {
            position: absolute;
            right: 8px;
            bottom: 8px;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: var(--ai-gradient);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .send-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Topbar -->
    <header class="topbar">
        <div class="topbar-left">
            <a href="/Home/AssignmentDetail" class="back-btn">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Cancel
            </a>
            <div class="ai-status-badge">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> AI Generated Assignment
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="topbar-right">
            <button class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-left"></i> Discard Draft</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Approve & Publish</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="staging-container">
        
        <!-- Left: Editor Content -->
        <div class="editor-col">
            
            <div class="ai-banner">
                <div class="ai-banner-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles"></i></div>
                <div class="ai-banner-content">
                    <h4>Review Assignment Draft</h4>
                    <p>The AI has generated the assignment instructions and a grading rubric based on your prompt. Please review and adjust the point distributions or instructions before publishing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <input type="text" class="title-input" value="Build a Weather Dashboard using React">

            <!-- Prompt/Instructions Editor -->
            <div class="card-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    Assignment Instructions
                </div>
                <div class="editor-toolbar">
                    <button class="toolbar-btn active"><i class="fa-solid fa-bold"></i></button>
                    <button class="toolbar-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-italic"></i></button>
                    <button class="toolbar-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-ul"></i></button>
                    <button class="toolbar-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i></button>
                </div>
                <div class="editor-content" contenteditable="true">
                    <h3>Project Overview</h3>
                    <p>In this assignment, you will build a React application that fetches and displays weather data from a public API (e.g., OpenWeatherMap). This project will test your understanding of React Hooks (useState, useEffect), API fetching, and component structuring.</p>
                    <br>
                    <h3>Requirements</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Allow users to search for a city by name.</li>
                        <li>Display the current temperature, humidity, and weather conditions.</li>
                        <li>Implement a 5-day forecast.</li>
                        <li>Handle loading states and API errors gracefully.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <br>
                    <h3>Submission Format</h3>
                    <p>Please submit a link to your public GitHub repository containing the source code, along with a link to a live deployed version (Vercel, Netlify, or GitHub Pages).</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Rubric Editor -->
            <div class="card-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    Grading Rubric
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary);">Total: 100 Pts</span>
                </div>
                <table class="rubric-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width: 25%;">Criteria</th>
                            <th style="width: 60%;">Description</th>
                            <th style="width: 15%; text-align: center;">Points</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><input type="text" value="Functionality"></td>
                            <td><input type="text" value="App correctly fetches and displays weather data for a searched city."></td>
                            <td style="text-align: center;"><input type="number" class="pts-input" value="40"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><input type="text" value="Code Quality"></td>
                            <td><input type="text" value="Proper use of React Hooks, components are well-structured and reusable."></td>
                            <td style="text-align: center;"><input type="number" class="pts-input" value="30"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><input type="text" value="UI/UX Design"></td>
                            <td><input type="text" value="The interface is clean, responsive, and handles loading/error states."></td>
                            <td style="text-align: center;"><input type="number" class="pts-input" value="20"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><input type="text" value="Deployment"></td>
                            <td><input type="text" value="The application is successfully deployed to a live URL."></td>
                            <td style="text-align: center;"><input type="number" class="pts-input" value="10"></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <div style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #fafafa; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i> Add Criterion</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Right: AI Assistant Panel -->
        <div class="ai-col">
            
            <div class="assistant-card">
                <div class="assistant-header">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i> EduNexus Copilot
                </div>

                <div class="prompt-info">
                    <div class="prompt-label">Original Prompt</div>
                    <div class="prompt-bubble">
                        "Generate a coding assignment for React students where they build a Weather Dashboard. Include technical requirements, submission guidelines, and a grading rubric worth 100 points."
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="suggestions-list">
                    <div class="prompt-label" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Refinement Actions</div>
                    
                    <div class="suggestion-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">
                            <strong>Add Bonus Challenge</strong><br>
                            Generate an extra credit requirement (e.g. Geolocation).
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="suggestion-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">
                            <strong>Expand Rubric</strong><br>
                            Break down the rubric into more granular 10-point criteria.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="suggestion-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">
                            <strong>Add Constraints</strong><br>
                            Add specific technical constraints (e.g. "Do not use Redux").
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="ai-chat-input">
                    <div class="prompt-label" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Talk to Copilot</div>
                    <div class="chat-box">
                        <textarea class="chat-textarea" placeholder="E.g. Change the submission format to require a ZIP file instead of GitHub..."></textarea>
                        <button class="send-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </main>

</body>
</html>
